# New Alchemical Discoveries
# ==============================

Directed Bomb				KEY:Discovery ~ Directed Bomb								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:The alchemist can cause his bombs to splash in a 15-foot cone instead of a 5-foot-radius burst. This discovery can't be combined with the explosive bomb discovery.
Elemental Mutagen (Air)		KEY:Discovery ~ Elemental Mutagen (Air)						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:Whenever the alchemist imbibes a mutagen, he gains resistance 5 to electricity and a +2 competence bonus on Fly checks. This resistance increases by 5 and the competence bonus by 2 for each of the following discoveries the alchemist possesses: grand mutagen, greater mutagen, and true mutagen. An alchemist can gain the benefits of only one elemental mutagen at a time, selected when he imbibes the mutagen.
Elemental Mutagen (Earth)	KEY:Discovery ~ Elemental Mutagen (Earth)					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:Whenever the alchemist imbibes a mutagen, he gains resistance 5 to acid and a +2 competence bonus on Climb checks. This resistance increases by 5 and the competence bonus by 2 for each of the following discoveries the alchemist possesses: grand mutagen, greater mutagen, and true mutagen. An alchemist can gain the benefits of only one elemental mutagen at a time, selected when he imbibes the mutagen.
Elemental Mutagen (Fire)	KEY:Discovery ~ Elemental Mutagen (Fire)					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:Whenever the alchemist imbibes a mutagen, he gains resistance 5 to fire and a +2 competence bonus on Acrobatics checks. This resistance increases by 5 and the competence bonus by 2 for each of the following discoveries the alchemist possesses: grand mutagen, greater mutagen, and true mutagen. An alchemist can gain the benefits of only one elemental mutagen at a time, selected when he imbibes the mutagen.
Elemental Mutagen (Water)	KEY:Discovery ~ Directed BombElemental Mutagen (Water)		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:Whenever the alchemist imbibes a mutagen, he gains resistance 5 to cold and a +2 competence bonus on Swim checks. This resistance increases by 5 and the competence bonus by 2 for each of the following discoveries the alchemist possesses: grand mutagen, greater mutagen, and true mutagen. An alchemist can gain the benefits of only one elemental mutagen at a time, selected when he imbibes the mutagen.
Healing Bomb*				KEY:Discovery ~ Healing Bomb								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DESC:Creating a healing bomb requires the alchemist to expend an infused extract (APG 31) or potion containing a cure spell. A creature that takes a direct hit from a healing bomb is healed as if she had imbibed the infusion or potion used to create the bomb. Creatures in the splash radius are healed for the minimum amount of damage the cure spell is capable of healing. A healing bomb damages undead instead of healing them.

