Discord						KEY:Witch Hex ~ Discord						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MinorHex					PREVARGTEQ:WitchHexAbilityLVL,1								SOURCEPAGE:p.28		DESC:The witch can make an animal or humanoid within 30 feet distrust another creature within line of sight. The target's attitude toward the other creature decreases		DESC: by one step. |PREVARLT:WitchLVL,8		DESC: by two steps. |PREVARGTEQ:WitchLVL,8		DESC:A successful Will save negates this effect. The effect lasts for %1 rounds. The duration can be extended with the cackle hex. Whether or not the save is successful, a creature cannot be the target of this hex again for 1 day.|INT
Major Hex - Pariah			KEY:Witch Major Hex ~ Pariah				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MajorHex					PREVARGTEQ:WitchHexAbilityLVL,10							SOURCEPAGE:p.28		DESC:The witch can cause a creature within 60 feet to be shunned by its allies for %1 rounds. Any other creature attempting to directly assist the target with a harmless spell or aid another action must attempt a Will save. If the save succeeds, the aiding creature is unaffected by this hex. If the save fails, the aiding creature can't follow through, the action is lost, and the aiding creature can't directly aid the target for the duration of this hex. This hex does not prevent the target from benefiting from area of effect spells.|INT
Grand Hex - Abominate		KEY:Witch Grand Hex ~ Abominate				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Spelllike.WitchHex.GrandHex						PREVARGTEQ:WitchHexAbilityLVL,18							SOURCEPAGE:p.28		DESC:The witch transforms a creature within 30 feet into an aberration. This hex acts as baleful polymorph, except the target is transmuted into a Small, Medium, or Large aberration. The target's abilities are modified as monstrous physique IV. Whether or not its save is successful, a creature cannot be the target of this hex again for 1 day.



